metadata.Author: Demandbase, Inc.
metadata.Readme:
Before starting, be sure your Demandbase subscription is current and have its API key ready.
1. Run installation procedure:
There are no Sitecore items involved in the module package. The entirety of the module is self-contained through initialise pipeline procedures. This means if something is accidentally deleted it can be easily repaired with a simple recycle of the app pool.
2. Configure the module:
Installing the module will place a configuration file in Sitecore at App_Config/Include called Demandbase.config. Inside this config is an XML node. Enter your Demandbase API access key into this node and save. This will recycle the app pool as well.
